  "prob_desc_output_spec": "Output the minimal amount of burles organizers should pay to satisfy all the delegations (i.e. to make the number of the boxes be divisible by $$$m$$$). It is allowed that the final number of the boxes is equal to $$$0$$$.",
  "source_code": "#include<stdio.h>\nint main()\n{\n    long long int c,a,n,m,b,d,e,f;\n    scanf(\"%lld%lld%lld%lld\",&n,&m,&a,&b);\n    c=n%m;\n    d=m-n%m;\n    b=b*c;\n    a=a*d;\n    if(a>b)\n        printf(\"%lld\\n\",b);\n    else\n        printf(\"%lld\\n\",a);\n    return 0;\n}\n",
